<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idbf12bb9e-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa" identifier="/us/usc/t42/s10143"><num value="10143">§ 10143.</num><heading> Title to material</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">Delivery, and acceptance by the Secretary, of any high-level radioactive waste or spent nuclear fuel for a repository constructed under this part shall constitute a transfer to the Secretary of title to such waste or spent fuel.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="idbf12bb9f-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa">(<ref href="/us/pl/97/425/tI/s123">Pub. L. 97–425, title I, § 123</ref>, <date date="1983-01-07">Jan. 7, 1983</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/96/2229">96 Stat. 2229</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
</section>
